Without any un-staged changes:

```bash
git tag -s typesafe-builders@v0.4.0 -m "typesafe-builders v0.4.0"
git tag -s typesafe-builders-core@v0.4.0 -m "typesafe-builders-core v0.4.0"
git tag -s typesafe-builders-derive@v0.4.0 -m "typesafe-builders-derive v0.4.0"

cargo publish -p typesafe-builders-core && cargo publish -p typesafe-builders-derive && cargo publish -p typesafe-builders
```
